pauseGame() - Method in class main.GameUIController
Pauses the game by stopping the logic's bgThread and bringing up a pause menu;
PrefsHighScores - Class in dynamicStorage
This class holds all of the player's preferred settings and the high scores for the particular program that the player is using.
PrefsHighScores() - Constructor for class dynamicStorage.PrefsHighScores
Creates a new PrefsHighScores object; THIS SHOULD ONLY BE USED IF THERE IS NOT ALREADY ONE OF THESE OBJECTS PRESENT! AFTER CREATING THIS OBJECT IT WILL BE SERIALIZED INTO A FILE AND RELOADED EACH TIME THE PROGRAM RUNS SO IT WILL NEVER NEED TO BE CONSTRUCTED AGAIN.
prefsHighScores - Static variable in class main.MAIN
Stores the PrefsHighScores object
